  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to learn about the effects of long term carnitine use in
      patients with metabolic disorders and its potential relationship to cardiovascular events.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This online cross-sectional survey will examine the self-reported long-term carnitine use in
      patients with metabolic disorders and any potential relationship to cardiovascular events.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
